  "detailed_description": "<strong>ZIC: Zombies In City</strong> is a first person zombie survival shooter where you have to save the world from a pandemic zombie apocalypse!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.poster.avif?t=1768536234\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.webm?t=1768536234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.mp4?t=1768536234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The undead zombies come out of a fog at night. Zombie infection spread throughout the city and initiated a zombie apocalypse. Walking dead everywhere... The deadly virus hasn't touched only some of people and it's the last hope for humanity. <br><br>Life will bring together 4 different characters in the zombie killer squad able to withstand the onslaught of the walking dead! They must stop a pandemic zombie infection with weapons!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/7a6452fe24985d78eac16e81cfc6967e.avif?t=1768536234\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Genre – first person zombie survival shooter<br></li><li> Story mode – interesting storyline about escaped survivors<br></li><li> Zombie killer squad – 4 heroes with unique character and history like in left 4 dead<br></li><li> 10 different zombie types, monsters and enemy marauder<br></li><li> Large selection of deadly weapons – chainsaw, uzi, grenade, rocket launcher, AK-47, baton, machete, bat, pistol & revolver</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>ZIC: Zombies In City</strong> is a first person zombie survival shooter where you have to save the world from a pandemic zombie apocalypse!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.poster.avif?t=1768536234\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.webm?t=1768536234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/3ba4104cb35a622b5ac097006215ad62.mp4?t=1768536234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The undead zombies come out of a fog at night. Zombie infection spread throughout the city and initiated a zombie apocalypse. Walking dead everywhere... The deadly virus hasn't touched only some of people and it's the last hope for humanity. <br><br>Life will bring together 4 different characters in the zombie killer squad able to withstand the onslaught of the walking dead! They must stop a pandemic zombie infection with weapons!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1051290/extras/7a6452fe24985d78eac16e81cfc6967e.avif?t=1768536234\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Genre – first person zombie survival shooter<br></li><li> Story mode – interesting storyline about escaped survivors<br></li><li> Zombie killer squad – 4 heroes with unique character and history like in left 4 dead<br></li><li> 10 different zombie types, monsters and enemy marauder<br></li><li> Large selection of deadly weapons – chainsaw, uzi, grenade, rocket launcher, AK-47, baton, machete, bat, pistol & revolver</li></ul>",
